<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TT1.10">
<l>punti kalaṅki matima yaṅki yiṟantava raippuṟaṅ kāṭṭi liṭṭuc</l>
<l>cantiyil vaittuk kaṭamai ceytu takkava riṭṭacen tīvi ḷakkā</l>
<l>munti yamarar muḻavi ṉōcai ticaikatu vaccilam pārkka vārkka</l>
<l>vantiyiṉ mānaṭa māṭu meṅka ḷappa ṉiṭamtiru vālaṅ kāṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of our father who dances the great dance at twilight,</l>
<l>while [his] anklets keep roaring, while the directions are perturbed by the sound of the immortals’ drums in front,</l>
<l>with the red fires as a light that were put up by those fit for it, doing [their] duty, placing [them] on junctions,</l>
<l>putting those who have died, understanding confounded, minds confused, on the cremation field outside,</l>
<l>is Tiruvalaṅkāṭu.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
